  * Fix a syntax error in manual page
  * Fix open() calls

 -- Vincent Bernat <bernat@luffy.cx>

lldpd (0.2)

  * Add privilege separation
  * Add FDP support
  * Support CDP encapsulated into native VLAN
  * Various fixes

 -- Vincent Bernat <bernat@luffy.cx>

